Furthermore, the paper may fall under the "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence) sub-category as it involves the use of machine learning techniques to solve a natural language processing problem. 

The "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval) sub-category is also a possibility as the paper involves retrieval methods for inducing word translation pairs.
